      "_type": "richTextSection",
      "backgroundImage": null,
      "content": [
        {
          "_key": "p1",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "p1s1",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "C-4 Flow is a welcoming, beginner-friendly pole and exotic dance studio centered on movement as self-expression. Our classes help you build strength, flexibility, and confidence while reconnecting with your body. You might come to train athletically, explore sensual movement, or simply move in a way that feels good."
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "normal"
        },
        {
          "_key": "badbeb49551e",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "p1s1",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "We believe dance is about more than tricks or choreography. It's about expression, emotion, and empowerment. At C-4 Flow, you're invited to show up as you are and move in ways that feel authentic to you: powerful, playful, seductive, soft, or bold."
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "normal"
        },
        {
          "_key": "p3",
          "_type": "block",
          "children": [
            {
              "_key": "p3s1",
              "_type": "span",
              "marks": [],
              "text": "Our studio is a supportive, judgment-free space built around community. From your very first class through every step of your pole journey, you'll find encouragement, respect, and room to grow at your own pace."
            }
          ],
          "markDefs": [],
          "style": "normal"
        },
        {
